# [color=#cfe2f3][b][size=4]What is This mod ?[/size][/b] [/color]#
This mod is standalone follower mod. You don't need other mods :D
Kinzie can be found at the "Braidwood Inn" in Kynesgrove.

She is good at bow and sneaking. She is Essential.
Her Body Type is UNP.
She is mixed race Nord and Wood Elf.

[color=#cc4125][size=4][b]日本語版espあるよ[/b][/size][/color]

btw, I have made ​​a mod, this is the first time.
If there is a place which does not load, please contact me.
